"<guimenuitem>Om &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> og <guimenuitem>Om &kde;</"
"guimenuitem> (eller <guimenuitem>Om &Qt;</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the &kde; desktop version, there is also an option to report a Bug or "
#| "Wishlist item."
msgid "There is also an option to report a Bug or Wishlist item."
msgstr ""
"I versionen for &kde;-desktoppen, er der også et punkt til at rapportere en "
"fejl eller et ønske."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you would like to make a suggestion or you have some new levels to "
#| "contribute, the current author's email address is in the "
#| "<guimenuitem>About &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgid ""
"If you would like to make a suggestion or you have some new levels to "
"contribute, the current author's email address is in the <guimenuitem>About "
